Name

wvCleanLatex - convert msword documents to LaTeX

Synopsis

wvCleanLatex in_word_doc out_latex_doc

Description

wvCleanLatex converts word documents into LaTeX that looks like it’d been hand-edited

More Information

http://wvware.sourceforge.net
